{"tid":1026582,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"蘇斯克查：A山狀態就像支茄汁","createTime":"2019-02-18T08:29:21.000Z","updateTime":"2019-02-18T15:05:36.000Z","uid":27851,"like":16,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":26,"replies":[{"pid":"4ad543f4ce306944f7b3837c070a215ab47e9f59","tid":1026582,"uid":27851,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T08:29:21.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/0ZLsbiY.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F0ZLsbiY.png&h=8d326cf9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n曼聯領隊蘇斯克查表示，狀態低沉的前鋒阿歷斯山齊士就像一支茄汁，當回勇時好表現就會不斷湧出來。<br />\n<br />\n史高斯撐蘇B值得坐正<br />\n「A山」上仗歐聯16強首回合面對巴黎聖日耳門，後備落場表現令人失望，而隨著馬迪爾及連格同樣因傷缺陣2至3星期，「A山」接下來的表現將更為重要。<br />\n<br />\n對此「蘇B」說︰「他是個充滿才華的球員，只要再次入波便可重拾信心，他就像支茄汁，起初你倒它時不會出來，但一出來便會湧過不停，我相信他將會很好。」<br />\n<br />\n「我們需要球員一直表現出最佳水平，曼聯要挑戰前4名，挑戰強隊，要有好演出至季尾。對PSG一仗或令球隊信心受挫，但我相信他們會在周一足總盃反彈。」(<a href=\"http://Goal.com\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2FGoal.com&d=8lKb2kYWDOzPE5G8cc2TgG58GJy%2FOqJThDagGYh0BQk%3D&h=e0e5452b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">Goal.com</a>)"},{"pid":"c23c27db65efd88f526623591f46e61bd0244105","tid":1026582,"uid":141519,"like":25,"dislike":6,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T08:32:44.000Z","msg":"唔緊要啦 曼聯攞硬冠軍 利物浦快收皮"},{"pid":"a57a4e9400b18e1aed008c9f0b4abc333bd1598b","tid":1026582,"uid":38456,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T08:33:52.000Z","msg":"支持"},{"pid":"1b8f8d590562c658b1e10ffa159a6ac3fc692724","tid":1026582,"uid":27851,"like":25,"dislike":2,"score":23,"quote":{"pid":"c23c27db65efd88f526623591f46e61bd0244105","tid":1026582,"uid":141519,"like":25,"dislike":6,"score":19,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T08:32:44.000Z","msg":"唔緊要啦 曼聯攞硬冠軍 利物浦快收皮"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-02-18T08:34:01.000Z","msg":"系 你班臭猁睇路 等我地牙山狀態好返實噴到你班廢柴一面都係<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pi